ColdFusion CAS Component Test App
=================================

Installation
------------
1. Add this entry to jrun-web.xml

    <virtual-mapping>
      <resource-path>/cfcas_test_app</resource-path>
      <system-path>/Users/johndzak/working_copies/coldfusion_cas_client/test_application</system-path>
    </virtual-mapping>    

2. Configure cas_server, in Application.cfc, to point to your CAS instance. 

3. [Optional] If you are using proxy ticketing, cas_proxy_callback_receive and cas_proxy_callback_retrieve, in Application.cfc, to point to your proxy ticketing callback application. 